type: TS LF Trading Bot Error - Stage Quoted Asset Node Missing

definition.text: A Stage Quoted Asset node was expected but not found at the node where the error originated.

translations.text: Bir Aşamalı Koteli Varlık ( Stage Quoted Asset ) düğümü bekleniyordu, ancak hatanın kaynaklandığı düğümde bulunamadı.
Ein Stage Quoted Asset -Knoten wurde erwartet, aber an dem Knoten, von dem der Fehler ausging, nicht gefunden.
Aşamalı Alıntı Varlık Düğümü Eksik. ( Stage Quoted Asset Node Missing )
Stage Quoted Asset-Knoten fehlt (Stage Quoted Asset Node Missing)

paragraphs.text: Add the missing node and try again.

translations.text: Eksik düğümü ekleyin ve tekrar deneyin.
Fügen Sie den fehlenden Knoten hinzu und versuchen Sie es erneut.
